  <entry>
    <title>Ubuntu 15.4 安装 WebStorm</title>
    <link href="http://www.gyzhao.me/2016/04/05/Ubuntu-Install-WebStorm/"/>
    <id>http://www.gyzhao.me/2016/04/05/Ubuntu-Install-WebStorm/</id>
    <published>2016-04-05T14:50:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-01-08T05:13:53.314Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>WebStorm是一个基于Java的跨平台的商业Web前端开发工具，这里告诉我们如何在Ubuntu中安装WebStorm。</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="安装-Oracle-JDK"><a href="#安装-Oracle-JDK" class="headerlink" title="安装 Oracle JDK"></a>安装 Oracle JDK</h3><p>WebStorm是基于Java的,我们需要安装Oracle JDK的支持,使用如下命令来安装:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/java</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install oracle-java7-installer</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install oracle-java7-set-default</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>运行命令查看是否安装成功:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java -version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>出现如下内容则表示安装成功:<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Picked up JAVA_TOOL_OPTIONS: -javaagent:/usr/share/java/jayatanaag.jar </span><br><span class="line">java version &quot;1.7.0_80&quot;</span><br><span class="line">Java(TM) SE Runtime Environment (build 1.7.0_80-b15)</span><br><span class="line">Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM (build 24.80-b11, mixed mode)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="安装-WebStorm"><a href="#安装-WebStorm" class="headerlink" title="安装 WebStorm"></a>安装 WebStorm</h3><p>首先需要下载WebStrom的Linux安装包,地址如下:<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/download/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>然后运行如下命令解压并安装并运行WebStorm:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar xfz ~/Downloads/WebStorm-10.0.4.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo mv ~/Downloads/WebStorm-141.1550 /opt/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /opt/WebStorm-141.1550/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> bin/</span><br><span class="line">sh webstorm.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="参考链接"><a href="#参考链接" class="headerlink" title="参考链接"></a>参考链接</h3><p><a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/help/system-requirements-and-installation.html#d173174e222" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/help/system-requirements-and-installation.html#d173174e222</a><br><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/16263556/installing-java-7-on-ubuntu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://stackoverflow.com/questions/16263556/installing-java-7-on-ubuntu</a></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;WebStorm是一个基于Java的跨平台的商业Web前端开发工具，这里告诉我们如何在Ubuntu中安装WebStorm。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
